---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof for Caterers — Testimonials That Fill Your Calendar | SocialProof">
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="badge">For Caterers</div>
      <h1>Your Best Events Should Be Your Best Marketing</h1>
      <p class="subhead">Couples, planners, and corporate clients research catering extensively before booking. Vouch puts authentic testimonials from your real events on your website — automatically building the trust that converts inquiries into contracts.</p>
      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
        <a href="/for" class="btn-secondary">See all industries →</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pain">
      <h2>Why Catering Is Hard to Market Without Testimonials</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Clients can't taste your food before booking — they rely entirely on what others say</li>
        <li>High ticket size means buyers do extensive research; a thin testimonial section kills conversions</li>
        <li>Wedding clients ask other brides; corporate clients ask other coordinators — word of mouth is your #1 channel</li>
        <li>After an event, you're busy breaking down — chasing testimonials is the last thing on your mind</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="solution">
      <h2>How Vouch Works for Caterers</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Create your collect link</strong> — one link, never changes, you use it forever</li>
        <li><strong>Send it after every event</strong> — add it to your invoice follow-up email or thank-you message</li>
        <li><strong>Clients submit in 60 seconds</strong> — no account needed, just their name and words</li>
        <li><strong>Approve and display</strong> — embed on your website with one script tag</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="social-proof-for-sp">
      <h2>What Caterers Say About Vouch</h2>
      <blockquote>
        <p>"I put the collect link in my post-event thank-you email. Three weeks later I had 20 new testimonials. My inquiry rate doubled — people trust the reviews more than anything I write about myself."</p>
        <cite>— Full-service caterer, Chicago IL</cite>
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote>
        <p>"Corporate clients want to see who you've worked with. Having 30+ real testimonials on my site is the single biggest conversion tool I have."</p>
        <cite>— Corporate catering company, Austin TX</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </section>

    <section class="use-cases">
      <h2>Built for Every Type of Catering Business</h2>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card"><strong>Wedding caterers</strong><p>Turn every bride into a referral engine. Their testimonial appears on your site before the next couple even calls.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><strong>Corporate caterers</strong><p>Build a portfolio of Fortune 500 and SMB testimonials. Show new prospects the names they recognize.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><strong>Event caterers</strong><p>From birthday parties to galas — every satisfied host is a marketing asset. Capture their words while the event is fresh.</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq">
      <h2>Common Questions</h2>
      <details>
        <summary>When should I send the collect link?</summary>
        <p>24–72 hours after the event when the memory is fresh and emotions are high. Include it in your thank-you email or final invoice. Timing matters — the longer you wait, the less likely you get a response.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I display testimonials by event type?</summary>
        <p>You can create separate widgets for weddings, corporate events, and private parties. Each widget pulls from your testimonial pool filtered as you choose.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What does it cost?</summary>
        <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. Upgrade to Pro ($19/mo) for multiple widgets, custom styling, and priority support.</p>
      </details>
    </section>

    <section class="final-cta">
      <h2>Let Every Event Sell the Next One</h2>
      <p>Set up your testimonial widget in minutes. Free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
      <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Get started free</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
